@page
@model ContosoCrafts.WebSite.Pages.FAQModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Frequently Asked Questions";
}

<!-- FAQ Container -->
<div class="container mt-5 text-center">

    <!-- Page Title -->
    <h1 class="display-3 text-white fw-bold contact-subheading">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>

    <!-- FAQ Items -->
    <div class="row mt-5 justify-content-center">

        <div class="col-md-10 p-4 bg-dark bg-opacity-75 rounded-4 text-white shadow-lg">
            <div class="faq-item mb-4">
                <h4 class="text-warning mb-2 contact-subheading"><i class="fas fa-question-circle"></i> What is the Avengers Encyclopedia?</h4>
                <p>It's your ultimate guide to Earth's mightiest heroes—featuring profiles, history, powers, and fun quizzes.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item mb-4">
                <h4 class="text-warning mb-2 contact-subheading"><i class="fas fa-question-circle"></i> How do I discover which Avenger I'm most like?</h4>
                <p>Take our interactive quiz by answering five themed questions—your Avenger match will be revealed!</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item mb-4">
                <h4 class="text-warning mb-2 contact-subheading"><i class="fas fa-question-circle"></i> Can I add my favorite hero to the site?</h4>
                <p>Absolutely! Use the 'Create New Hero' feature to contribute a hero profile to the encyclopedia.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item mb-4">
                <h4 class="text-warning mb-2 contact-subheading"><i class="fas fa-question-circle"></i> Are the superhero stats official?</h4>
                <p>Stats are based on a mix of movies, comics, and fan interpretations—this is a fan project for entertainment purposes!</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item mb-4">
                <h4 class="text-warning mb-2 contact-subheading"><i class="fas fa-question-circle"></i> How often is the website updated?</h4>
                <p>We aim to add new heroes and features regularly—stay tuned for updates!</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item mb-4">
                <h4 class="text-warning mb-2 contact-subheading"><i class="fas fa-question-circle"></i> Is there a comparison feature for superheroes?</h4>
                <p>Yes! You can compare heroes side by side to see who would win in a showdown—try it out!</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item mb-4">
                <h4 class="text-warning mb-2 contact-subheading"><i class="fas fa-question-circle"></i> Can I filter heroes by their abilities?</h4>
                <p>Yes! Use the filter options to explore heroes based on specific powers and traits.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item mb-4">
                <h4 class="text-warning mb-2 contact-subheading"><i class="fas fa-question-circle"></i> What should I do if I find an error or bug?</h4>
                <p>Let us know! Use the 'Contact' page to report bugs or suggest improvements.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item mb-4">
                <h4 class="text-warning mb-2 contact-subheading"><i class="fas fa-question-circle"></i> Are there any upcoming features planned?</h4>
                <p>Yes! We're working on adding a hero battle simulator, user login, and fan art gallery—stay tuned!</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <h4 class="text-warning mb-2 contact-subheading"><i class="fas fa-question-circle"></i> Can I share this website with my friends?</h4>
                <p>Of course! Feel free to share the link and invite others to discover their Avenger!</p>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>

</div>
